        <mxCell id="tHcQaHCFfMApkivgtKiR-1" value="Soa vs MS:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. reusability Vs data duplication:&lt;br&gt;reusability : (SOA: services are the reusable components i.e. ==&amp;gt; &lt;b&gt;scaling and efficiency.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;agility :&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;fault tolerance :&amp;nbsp;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=22;" vertex="1" parent="1">
